title: Forsaken Palace of Ahra
story: For centuries the palace of Ahra was considered lost. Lately a huge mutant eagle has made its home here. It is said that Tyroxos-Skaz, a legendary rod, is hidden here.

notes.text: A large gate with three keyholes to the north.
A key in a magically locked curio case.
A key tucked under some debris.
An amulet of invocation in a chest.
Remains of an orc, a key in his hands.
